\cf0 $ffc100 create disk image from source (effective address) string:\par
Name, Sides, TracksPerSide, SectorsPerTrack, each ending with /0\par
$ffc104 leave emu detect\par
$ffc105 set cpu speed in mhz\par
$ffc107 snapshot loaded\par
$ffc108 set run speed (in %)\par
$ffc10a write byte\par

\pard{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf8\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa160\sl252\slmult1 $4D ('M') informs Steem that D5 contains the address of mouse coordinates, to be displayed in the status bar\par
{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}$51 ('Q') to quit Steem\par
{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}$52 ('R') to reboot (cold reset)\par
{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}$51 ('r') to reset\par
{\pntext\f8\'B7\tab}$53 ('S') to stop emulation\par

